  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">KPMG - Trocaire Internal Management and Control</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">KPMG - Trocaire Internal Management and Control</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Revisionens syfte &#xE4;r att s&#xE4;kerst&#xE4;lla att insatsen &#x201C;Trocaire, Building Gender Equitable and Resilience in Ituri, DRC&#x201D; hanteras i enlighet med det s&#xE4;rskilda avtalet mellan Sida, genom den Svenska Ambassaden i DR Kongo och Troicare, &#xE4;ven genom dess lokalkontor i DR Kongo (11191). 

Detta uppdrag kommer att ge en &#xF6;verblick &#xF6;ver Tr&#xF3;caire&#x2019;s eventuella svagheter och styrkor avseende styrning och kontroll. Baserat p&#xE5; resultaten fr&#xE5;n revisionen kommer ambassaden att kr&#xE4;va att Tr&#xF3;caire, f&#xF6;re och under avtalsperioden, &#xE5;tg&#xE4;rdar de svagheter som framkommit under revisionen. N&#xE5;gra av &#xE5;tg&#xE4;rderna kommer att inkluderas som i avtalet mellan Tr&#xF3;caire och Sida samt f&#xF6;ljas upp vid den &#xE5;rliga revisionen.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The assessment of the internal management and Control of Tr&#xF3;caire shall be carried out to ensure that the project entitled &quot;Trocaire, Building Gender Equitable and Resilience in Ituri, DRC&quot; have been handled in accordance with the Specific Agreement between the Swedish Embassy and  Tr&#xF3;caire office in DRC (11191).

This assignment will give an overview to the Embasssy to know more about eventual weaknesses and strengths of Tr&#xF3;caire. Based on the findings, the embassy will require that Tr&#xF3;caire (Irish NGO) addresses the weaknesses as appropriate before or during the agreement phase. Some of the measures will be included as agreement conditions to be followed up during the annual audit.</narrative>
  </description>
